Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.23,0:00:23.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,《星際迷航: 新世界》前情提要\N{\rENG}Previously on Star Trek: Strange New Worlds...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.80,0:00:24.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,艾麗卡傷勢嚴重 但傷情穩定了\N{\rENG}Erica is critical, but stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.06,0:00:29.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,我到現在都覺得像是在做夢\N{\rENG}Still doesn't feel totally real.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.44,0:00:30.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,我本該死了的\N{\rENG}I should be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.24,0:00:31.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,我還活著只是僥天之幸\N{\rENG}I'm on borrowed time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.36,0:00:32.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,我還沒準備好和你分別\N{\rENG}I'm not ready to let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.24,0:00:34.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,達克'拉赫將軍\N{\rENG}General Dak'Rah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:37.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,我知道你和查普爾都曾駐紮在加戈爾上\N{\rENG}I know you and Chapel were both stationed on J'Gal, 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:39.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,拉赫就是在那裡成名的\N{\rENG}where Rah earned his reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.91,0:00:44.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,姆'本加 我來這裡是為了給你提供療癒\N{\rENG}M'Benga, I'm here to provide healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.80,0:00:46.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,把你的手從我身上拿開\N{\rENG}Get your hands off me! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.92,0:00:48.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,不是我先動手的\N{\rENG}I didn't start the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.34,0:00:49.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,但我很高興他死了\N{\rENG}But I'm glad he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.36,0:01:01.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,艦長個人日誌\N{\rENG}Captain's personal log,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.60,0:01:04.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,星曆2449.1\N{\rENG}stardate 2449.1.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.02,0:01:06.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,進取號要去完成一個常規掃描任務\N{\rENG}Enterprise has embarked on a routine scanning mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.63,0:01:08.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,這給了我和瑪麗一些額外的相處時間\N{\rENG}giving Marie and me some time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.24,0:01:09.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,她很快就要去\N{\rENG}to enjoy our last few days together
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.89,0:01:11.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,新的船上任職了\N{\rENG}before her new commission.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:14.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,我才剛習慣她的裝飾風格\N{\rENG}I was just getting used to her decorating choices,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.46,0:01:16.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,但一位艦長終歸是屬於她自己的船的\N{\rENG}but a captain belongs on her own ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:26.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們原本以為\N{\rENG}We had every reason to believe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:29.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,那些難以捉摸的戈恩組織已完全萎縮\N{\rENG}the evasive Gorn tissue was in full remission.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.50,0:01:32.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,但不幸的是 它們復發了\N{\rENG}But, unfortunately, it's returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:34.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,而且呈現出高度侵襲性\N{\rENG}And it's aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.38,0:01:36.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是情況也不是完全無望\N{\rENG}And yet, hope is not lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.09,0:01:39.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,奇美拉之花\N{\rENG}The Chimera Blossom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:40.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,一個珍稀品種\N{\rENG}A rare specimen, 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.50,0:01:42.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,因其獨特的生物特性而備受追捧\N{\rENG}long sought-after for its biological uniqueness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.82,0:01:44.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,這種花 可以治好她嗎\N{\rENG}This flower-- it can help her?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.76,0:01:46.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,希望渺茫 克里斯\N{\rENG}It's a long shot, Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.19,0:01:47.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,但據傳\N{\rENG}But it is rumored
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.14,0:01:49.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,其中含有一種特殊化合物\N{\rENG}to contain a chemical compound
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.14,0:01:50.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,這種化合物普遍擁有\N{\rENG}that is universal in its ability
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.94,0:01:54.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,協助入侵分子穿透細胞膜的能力\N{\rENG}to move invasive molecules through cell membranes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:01:57.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,也許能遏制惡性腫瘤\N{\rENG}Could stop the malignancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.72,0:01:58.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,爭取治療的時間\N{\rENG}Buying us time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.58,0:02:00.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,為什麼我嗅到了弦外之音\N{\rENG}Why am I sensing a caveat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:02.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,正如史波克所說 它很稀有\N{\rENG}Well, like Spock said, it's rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.78,0:02:05.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們已經找到了一處\N{\rENG}And we've tracked down the one place
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.42,0:02:08.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,有可能長有奇美拉之花的地方\N{\rENG}the Chimera is likely to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.21,0:02:10.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,在一個叫肯佛瑞的星球\N{\rENG}It's a planet called Kenfori.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.04,0:02:11.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,肯佛瑞?\N{\rENG}Kenfori?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.18,0:02:13.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,那整個星系都禁止通航\N{\rENG}That whole system is a no-fly zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.08,0:02:14.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊 確實\N{\rENG}Yeah, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.35,0:02:16.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是那裡原先有一個\N{\rENG}But it was once the location
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.34,0:02:17.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,星聯的科研設施\N{\rENG}of a Federation research facility,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.96,0:02:19.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,主要致力於新興地區農業研究\N{\rENG}focused mainly on frontier farming,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.87,0:02:21.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,特別是作物長效培育技術\N{\rENG}specifically crop longevity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.31,0:02:23.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,後來在戰爭初期 那裡被克林貢占領了\N{\rENG}The Klingons invaded at the start of the war
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:25.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們的所有權有了爭議\N{\rENG}and our claim fell into dispute.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:29.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,戰爭結束之後 雙方都同意放棄爭奪此地\N{\rENG}After the war ended, both sides agreed to give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:31.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以這不僅是個禁航區域\N{\rENG}So it's not just a no-fly zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.06,0:02:32.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,還是個限制區域\N{\rENG}It's the restricted zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.11,0:02:35.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們去那裡的話\N{\rENG}We can't go anywhere near it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:36.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,會違反一堆外交條約\N{\rENG}without violating multiple treaties.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.89,0:02:38.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,我告訴過他們這個主意簡直瘋了 克里斯\N{\rENG}Told them it was crazy, Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.48,0:02:40.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不會讓大家為了我一個人冒這麼大的風險\N{\rENG}I won't allow people to take risks like this for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.90,0:02:42.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,我更不會眼睜睜地看著你死 \N{\rENG}I won't watch you die. 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:44.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果這種花能救治你 我們就要拿到它\N{\rENG}If this blossom will help you, we are going to get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.86,0:02:46.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是\N{\rENG}But
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.66,0:02:48.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,星際艦隊肯定不會批准這種事\N{\rENG}Starfleet will never authorize this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.51,0:02:50.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們得偷偷地幹這件事\N{\rENG}This has to be completely off the books.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:52.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以我們提議派一個小型外勤隊去\N{\rENG}That is why we propose a minimal away team.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.88,0:02:54.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,就姆'本加醫生和我去就行\N{\rENG}Just Dr. M'Benga and myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:02:56.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,計劃挺好\N{\rENG}Good plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.22,0:02:57.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,只需做一處調整\N{\rENG}With one adjustment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.96,0:02:58.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,看吧 要來了\N{\rENG}Here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:00.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果必須得有人為此違規 那也得是我\N{\rENG}If anyone's going to break the rules, it's going to be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:02.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,早就說他會這樣了吧\N{\rENG}Told them that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:04.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,我很感激你自願參與任務 史波克先生\N{\rENG}I appreciate you stepping up Mr. Spock,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.24,0:03:06.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是如果我們被發現了 責任在我\N{\rENG}but if we're caught, the responsibility falls on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.20,0:03:10.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,別小看我啊 艦長\N{\rENG}You insult me, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.88,0:03:12.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,他從來沒被發現過\N{\rENG}He never gets caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.10,0:03:15.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,我從來沒被發現過\N{\rENG}I never get caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:17.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,斯坎內爾中尉\N{\rENG}Lieutenant Scannell,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:18.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,請把肯佛瑞星系周圍\N{\rENG}please pull up cartography
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.45,0:03:19.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,緩衝帶的星圖調取出來\N{\rENG}on the buffer zone around the Kenfori system.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.92,0:03:23.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,看起來條約劃定的分界線\N{\rENG}Looks like the treaty line is
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:24.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,正處於一片巨型星塵帶的邊緣\N{\rENG}on the edge of a giant dust belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:26.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,我已經很久沒有飛進過\N{\rENG}Been a long time since I've flown
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:28.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,有爭議的克林貢星域了\N{\rENG}into disputed Klingon territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:30.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,是路過有爭議的克林貢星域\N{\rENG}Around disputed Klingon territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.77,0:03:32.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,進取號不會跨越分界線\N{\rENG}Enterprise will not cross that line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.64,0:03:34.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,一旦穿梭機飛進星塵帶\N{\rENG}Once the shuttle clears that dust belt,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:35.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,個人通訊將徹底中斷\N{\rENG}personal comms will be down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.38,0:03:37.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們可以通過凍結所有通訊信號\N{\rENG}We can maintain their cover by freezing all other 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.28,0:03:38.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,來給他們打掩護\N{\rENG}communications as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:40.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,我會設置一個加密的艦對艦頻道\N{\rENG}I'm setting up an encrypted ship-to-ship channel
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:42.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,這樣艦長就能和我們保持聯絡\N{\rENG}for the captain to check in on the hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:43.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,不需要我提醒你們 \N{\rENG}I do not need to remind you 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.64,0:03:46.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,一旦穿梭機被發現 會有什麼後果吧\N{\rENG}of the consequences if our away team's shuttle is discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.42,0:03:47.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,奧特加斯 我們出發吧\N{\rENG}Ortegas, take us out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.11,0:04:09.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,有趣的部分來了\N{\rENG}Now comes the fun part.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:23.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,顯擺\N{\rENG}Show-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.96,0:04:28.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,歡迎大家盡情誇獎 鼓掌喝彩\N{\rENG}I'll accept any and all accolades and applause
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.52,0:04:30.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,小費我也收哦\N{\rENG}and tips.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.61,0:04:33.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,承認吧 你們都懷念我精湛的駕駛技術\N{\rENG}Admit it. You all missed my fancy flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:35.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們確實懷念\N{\rENG}We did, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.03,0:04:54.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,就像騎自行車一樣\N{\rENG}Like riding a bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,只不過這自行車用的核聚變引擎\N{\rENG}With fusion-powered thrusters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:05:00.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,我以為你可恨我的飛行技術了\N{\rENG}And all this time I thought you hated my flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:04.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,你還記得在波瑞利斯ζ星那次嗎\N{\rENG}You remember Zeta Borealis?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:07.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,穿梭機落地的一瞬間\N{\rENG}The moment our shuttle landed,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.04,0:05:08.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,你一腳踢開防爆門\N{\rENG}you kicked open those storm doors
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.58,0:05:10.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,當場嘔吐了起來\N{\rENG}and you threw up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.74,0:05:15.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果我沒記錯的話 那是因為我們之前\N{\rENG}If memory serves, it was those Vedalan cigars
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:17.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,抽了維達蘭雪茄的緣故\N{\rENG}we smoked the night before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:21.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,不過說實話 那些維達蘭人辦的派對真是一絕\N{\rENG}Well, those Vedalans knew how to throw a party, let's be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:21.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,絕對的\N{\rENG}Oh, definitely
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.94,0:05:23.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,即使事後頭疼都值了\N{\rENG}worth the headache.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.86,0:05:27.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,在我們行進的路線上有一個物體\N{\rENG}Oh, there's an object in our path.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:28.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,成分無法確定\N{\rENG}Indeterminate composition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.60,0:05:30.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,星塵帶有干擾 沒法掃描\N{\rENG}Can't get a reading in this dust belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:32.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,戰爭期間 這種地方布滿了雙方布下的\N{\rENG}During the war this area would have been teeming with mines.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.82,0:05:34.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,太空雷陣\N{\rENG}Federation and Klingon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.76,0:05:36.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是根據條約 空雷應該被排除了才對\N{\rENG}Per the treaty, they should have all been swept.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.51,0:05:40.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,也許他們遺漏了一個\N{\rENG}Maybe they missed one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.04,0:05:45.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,我會與之保持距離 最好把護盾也升起來\N{\rENG}I'll keep a distance. Better raise shields.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:47.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,打開通訊系統\N{\rENG}Turn on comms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:50.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,正在將通訊系統設置為克林貢常用頻段\N{\rENG}Setting comms to common Klingon frequency range.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.09,0:05:57.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,這是一個通訊信標\N{\rENG}It's a communications beacon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.14,0:06:00.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,這裡有一條信息\N{\rENG}Something's coming through.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.58,0:06:04.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,你見過這個嗎\N{\rENG}You ever see that before?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:07.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊 在戰爭期間見過\N{\rENG}Yes, in the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.10,0:06:09.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,我曾被派駐到一座被炸毀的克林貢礦場附近\N{\rENG}I was once stationed near a bombed Klingon mine
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.38,0:06:11.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,那裡有嚴重的輻射危險\N{\rENG}with radiation danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:14.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,大致翻譯一下就{\fsp-50}是{\fsp0}「要麼滾回去 要麼等死」\N{\rENG}Loosely translated it means, "Go back or die."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:16.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,但他們為什麼要在這裡放警示信標\N{\rENG}But why leave a warning beacon here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.38,0:06:19.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,不管了\N{\rENG}It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:22.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們沒有退路\N{\rENG}Going back is not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.41,0:08:28.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,沒有生命跡象\N{\rENG}No life signs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.29,0:08:30.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以這裡除了我們 沒別人\N{\rENG}So we are all alone down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:32.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,不 艦長\N{\rENG}No, Captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.06,0:08:34.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,我是說完全沒有生命體徵\N{\rENG}I mean no life signs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.47,0:08:37.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,全是植物 沒有動物\N{\rENG}All flora, no fauna...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:39.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,如此富饒的生物群落中沒有動物嗎\N{\rENG}In a biome this rich?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:40.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,這裡肯定有地方存在著動物\N{\rENG}There must be animal life here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:43.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,算了 至少我們是來找植物的\N{\rENG}Well, at least the flora's all that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.56,0:08:45.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,你看到下山路上的那個湖了嗎\N{\rENG}You see that lake on the way down?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:47.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,看到了 非常適合飛釣\N{\rENG}Ah, perfect for fly-fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:49.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊 要是我們沒有在執行任務\N{\rENG}Yeah, if we weren't always on a mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.10,0:08:52.31,CHS,,0,0,0,,而且還得有動物能上鈎才行\N{\rENG}And if there was something alive to catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.10,0:08:54.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,有道理\N{\rENG}Fair point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.44,0:08:57.23,CHS,,0,0,0,,那應該就是我們的研究站了\N{\rENG}That must be our research facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:08:58.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,根據克莉絲汀的研究\N{\rENG}Christine's research suggests 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:09:01.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,他們應該會把那種花的樣本保存在內\N{\rENG}they would have kept samples of the flower inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.42,0:09:04.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,至少我們不用把整片森林翻個遍了\N{\rENG}At least we don't have to scour this whole forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:08.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以 你怎麼看科爾比和克里斯汀這對情侶\N{\rENG}So, what do you think of this whole Korby-Christine thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:09.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,哦 克里斯 \N{\rENG}Ah, Chris, 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:12.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,要我提醒你 我離過三次婚嗎\N{\rENG}do I have to remind you I have three ex-wives?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:13.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,準確來說是四個\N{\rENG}Well, four, technically.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:16.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,那一次不算\N{\rENG}That was an annulment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:17.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,不過下一位嘛\N{\rENG}But the next one...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.06,0:09:19.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,醫者可以自醫嗎\N{\rENG}Physician heal thyself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:22.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,我更願意說 我還在不斷進步中\N{\rENG}I like to consider myself a work in progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:24.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,有生命跡象了嗎\N{\rENG}Life sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:26.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,恰恰相反\N{\rENG}The opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.87,0:09:37.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,陣亡的士兵嗎\N{\rENG}War casualty?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:39.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\rENG}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:41.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,戰鬥中不可能會有這種創傷\N{\rENG}You don't see these wounds in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.08,0:09:43.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,他的胸腔被整個剖開了\N{\rENG}His rib cage has been split open.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:45.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,挨了不止一發相位槍\N{\rENG}Not a single phaser burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:46.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,從腐爛程度來看\N{\rENG}Given the rate of decay,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:48.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,我判斷他是在撤離之後死去的\N{\rENG}I'd say he died after the evacuation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:51.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,像是被什麼動物殺死的\N{\rENG}Killed by some kind of animal maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.34,0:09:52.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,只是\N{\rENG}Only...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.26,0:09:54.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,這裡沒有動物\N{\rENG}Only no life signs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.26,0:09:58.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,會是早已離開的動物嗎\N{\rENG}An animal that's long gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.12,0:10:00.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,最好不要冒這個險\N{\rENG}Better not risk it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:01.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,相位槍準備\N{\rENG}Phasers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:24.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,備用能源還在運作著\N{\rENG}Auxiliary power's still on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.26,0:10:28.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,十分微弱\N{\rENG}Barely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:30.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,這裡發生的事情真是令人遺憾\N{\rENG}It's a shame what happened here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.28,0:10:33.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,戰爭奪走了一切\N{\rENG}The war took everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.78,0:10:58.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,這個是奇美拉之花嗎\N{\rENG}Chimera Blossoms?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.96,0:11:05.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,親眼所見 果然更驚艷\N{\rENG}Even more beautiful in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:09.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,得來全不費功夫啊\N{\rENG}Didn't have to look far, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:10.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,別靠近\N{\rENG}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.93,0:11:19.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,你的背包裡有一個面罩\N{\rENG}There's a set of these in your bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:21.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,尋找那些盛開的花朵\N{\rENG}Look for the ones in full bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.33,0:11:23.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,但不要用皮膚直接接觸它們\N{\rENG}But don't touch them with bare skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.64,0:11:25.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,這些到底是什麼\N{\rENG}What exactly are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:27.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,只是預防措施而已\N{\rENG}It's just a precaution.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.64,0:11:32.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,劑量不當的話 藥物也可能具有毒性\N{\rENG}At improper doses, the medication can be toxic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:36.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,某些有機毒物具有藥用價值\N{\rENG}Certain organic poisons have medicinal value.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:38.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,幾個世紀以來 醫生們用這些\N{\rENG}Doctors have used them for centuries
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.48,0:11:39.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,來治療心臟疾病\N{\rENG}to treat heart disease,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.90,0:11:41.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,瘧疾\N{\rENG}malaria...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.79,0:11:47.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,這能讓她維持多久\N{\rENG}How long will this give her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:52.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,你知道 任何船員的病情和治療情況\N{\rENG}You know the condition and treatment of any crew member
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:54.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,都是保密的\N{\rENG}is confidential 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:57.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,除非他們會對其他船員構成威脅\N{\rENG}unless they jeopardize the rest of the crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.72,0:11:59.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不是在以艦長的身份問你\N{\rENG}Not as your captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.10,0:12:00.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,而是以一個朋友的身份\N{\rENG}As your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:02.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,以瑪麗的\N{\rENG}As Marie's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:04.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,我需要知道\N{\rENG}I need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:06.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,她有希望完全康復嗎\N{\rENG}I-Is there a chance that she can really be saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.64,0:12:10.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,這是她唯一康復的機會了\N{\rENG}This is her only chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:13.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,就在昨天 我們束手無策的時候\N{\rENG}Just yesterday, we were out of options,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:14.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,史波克又找到了一個治療方案\N{\rENG}but Spock found one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.99,0:12:16.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,一份希望\N{\rENG}One to hope for.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.03,0:12:19.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,克里斯 奮力一搏的機會\N{\rENG}A fighting chance, Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:56.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,檢測到一股輕微的電磁波動	\N{\rENG}Picking up a minor EM flux
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.18,0:12:57.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,正朝著肯佛瑞方向移動\N{\rENG}moving towards Kenfori.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.90,0:13:01.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,坐標 第八扇區 方位角15-29-4\N{\rENG}Coordinates: Section Eight, mark 15-29-4.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:04.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,傳感器顯示其在以一個不規則的運動軌跡移動\N{\rENG}Sensors show it is moving in an irregular pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.06,0:13:06.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,這表明這是一種自然發生的現象\N{\rENG}That suggests it's a naturally occurring phenomenon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:07.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,對於塵埃帶來說很正常\N{\rENG}Normal for a dust belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.06,0:13:10.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,收到 繼續觀察第九扇區\N{\rENG}Copy. Continue to Section Nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:12.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,長官 我提議對第八扇區進行二次掃描\N{\rENG}Commander, I would like to recommend a secondary scan
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.36,0:13:15.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,這一回濾除電磁信號\N{\rENG}of Section Eight, one that filters out EM rays.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.72,0:13:16.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,我有預感\N{\rENG}I've got a hunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.86,0:13:17.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,安全點總沒錯\N{\rENG}Better safe than sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:19.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,斯坎內爾中尉\N{\rENG}Lieutenant Scannell?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:20.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,重新掃描第八扇區\N{\rENG}Rescanning Section Eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:22.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,確認在電磁波動後方存在中微子輻射\N{\rENG}Confirming neutrino emissions behind the flux.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:23.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,正在檢測曲速信號\N{\rENG}Checking for a warp signature.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:29.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,是一艘克林貢戰列巡洋艦\N{\rENG}It's a Klingon battle cruiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:34.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,戰爭期間 他們經常使用電磁干擾\N{\rENG}In the war they used to mask their ships
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:36.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,來掩蓋他們的曲速信號\N{\rENG}behind bursts of EM radiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.36,0:13:37.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,幹得漂亮 上尉\N{\rENG}Good call, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:39.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,這改變不了什麼\N{\rENG}This doesn't change a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:40.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們繼續保持在此監視他們\N{\rENG}We continue monitoring from here
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:41.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,直到我們有理由接近\N{\rENG}until we have reason not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.44,0:13:43.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,中校 他們選擇現在露面\N{\rENG}Commander, it's a pretty big coincidence
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:44.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,是個巨大的巧合\N{\rENG}that they choose now to show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:46.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,要是他們發現了艦長的穿梭機怎麼辦\N{\rENG}What if they spotted the captain's shuttle?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:47.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,或許吧\N{\rENG}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.96,0:13:50.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,但克林貢人算不上有多遵守條約\N{\rENG}But Klingons aren't famous for abiding by treaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:52.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,他們可能只是來打撈殘骸的\N{\rENG}These could just be scavengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:54.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不喜歡在沒有證據的情況下妄下結論\N{\rENG}I hate to assume causation where there isn't any.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:56.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,烏乎拉 通訊上監聽到什麼東西嗎\N{\rENG}Uhura, any comms chatter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:58.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,沒有 長官 所有通訊頻段都處於靜默狀態\N{\rENG}Negative, sir, across all channels.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.46,0:14:00.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,外面安靜得像圖書館一樣\N{\rENG}It's quiet as a library out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.14,0:14:01.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,有變化的話向我報告\N{\rENG}Let me know if that changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.05,0:14:05.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,現在 我們要沉住氣\N{\rENG}For now... we'll sit tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:21.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,這些傷口與外面那些\N{\rENG}These wounds are consistent with
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:23.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,克林貢人遺骸上的傷口相符\N{\rENG}those Klingon remains outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:26.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,有什麼東西在同時殺害人類和克林貢人嗎\N{\rENG}Something was killing both humans and Klingons?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:28.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果可以稱之為殺害的話\N{\rENG}If you can call it that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.65,0:14:31.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,這更像是生吞活剝\N{\rENG}More like devouring.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:33.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,走吧 我們已經拿到需要的東西了\N{\rENG}Come on. We got what we came for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:34.39,CHS,,0,0,0,,撤退吧\N{\rENG}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.16,0:14:39.05,CHS,,0,0,0,,那肯定是個活物\N{\rENG}That had to be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.26,0:14:45.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,是發生故障的實驗室設備\N{\rENG}Malfunctioning lab equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.88,0:14:49.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,我還是沒有檢測到任何生命信號\N{\rENG}I'm still not getting any life signs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:51.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,不會吧\N{\rENG}Humor me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.15,0:14:58.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,什麼都沒有\N{\rENG}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:05.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們的穿梭機\N{\rENG}Our shuttle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:08.99,CHS,,0,0,0,,有可能他們不知道我們的存在\N{\rENG}It's possible they don't know about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.52,0:15:16.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,現在他們知道了\N{\rENG}They know about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.94,0:15:42.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}人類的惡臭在空氣中瀰漫不散
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:45.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}他們離得不遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.54,0:16:04.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}省著點用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:06.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}留著能量對付他們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:07.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}三錄儀給我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:15.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}他們說上去的人沒一個能活著回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:18.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}準備好為榮譽赴死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:22.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,這是場狩獵派對\N{\rENG}It's a hunting party.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.89,0:16:24.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,他們像獵斯克拉兔子一樣在追我們\N{\rENG}They're chasing us like Skral rabbits.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.89,0:16:25.26,Note,,0,0,0,,* 斯克拉是克林貢母星克洛諾斯北半球的一條河 在克林貢神話中曾變為血河
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.26,0:16:26.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果我們被抓住了\N{\rENG}If we're captured,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.11,0:16:28.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,他們肯定也很樂意把我們做成標本\N{\rENG}they'll want to make examples of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.99,0:16:37.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,我猜兩條路都一樣\N{\rENG}I'm sure the other direction was equally as bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:51.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,你知道他們看到了就會開槍\N{\rENG}You know they'll shoot on sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.96,0:16:53.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,那我們就先開槍\N{\rENG}Then we shoot first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.86,0:16:54.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,擊暈擋\N{\rENG}On stun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.85,0:18:35.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,快跑\N{\rENG}Run.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.32,0:18:23.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:44.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,你給我打的是安慰劑嗎\N{\rENG}Are you hitting me with placebo right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:47.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,你的身體已經適應了止痛藥\N{\rENG}Your body has acclimated to the pain inhibitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.16,0:18:49.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,查普爾護士應該可以\N{\rENG}Nurse Chapel should...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:51.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉\N{\rENG}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.06,0:18:54.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,巴特爾艦長\N{\rENG}Captain Batel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:56.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,我理解您的不適在加劇\N{\rENG}I understand your discomfort has increased.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.83,0:18:57.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,史波克\N{\rENG}Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.54,0:18:58.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,還用你說\N{\rENG}You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.52,0:19:00.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,瓦肯人有一種古代技藝\N{\rENG}Vulcans have an ancient technique
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:01.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,能通過冥想來調節疼痛\N{\rENG}of regulating pain through meditation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:03.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,經過練習 人類也可以掌握\N{\rENG}With practice, humans can do it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:04.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,儘管如此 要達到我認為您需要的水平\N{\rENG}However, achieving a level I suspect you need
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.92,0:19:06.27,CHS,,0,0,0,,需要的時間是我們等不起的\N{\rENG}will take time we do not have.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.27,0:19:08.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,查普爾護士建議我來引導您\N{\rENG}Nurse Chapel has suggested I guide you through it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.36,0:19:10.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,借助心靈融合的形式 如果您願意的話\N{\rENG}using a form of mind meld, if you consent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:11.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,什麼都行\N{\rENG}Pretty much anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.29,0:19:24.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,吾思即汝思\N{\rENG}My mind to your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:28.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,同呼吸共命運\N{\rENG}One breath between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:32.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,無論你在做什麼 請繼續\N{\rENG}Whatever you're doing, keep doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.54,0:19:35.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,是您的自尊心承受著痛苦\N{\rENG}Your ego holds the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.43,0:19:37.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,讓您的思想放下自尊心\N{\rENG}Let your mind release your ego,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:40.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,這樣或許可以減輕您的痛苦\N{\rENG}so it may eclipse your suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.24,0:20:02.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,史波克\N{\rENG}Spock!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.85,0:20:03.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,快醒醒\N{\rENG}Snap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:09.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,史波克 放開她 是我啊\N{\rENG}Let go of her, Spock. It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:10.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,克里斯汀\N{\rENG}It's Christine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.43,0:20:20.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,我似乎暫時情緒失控了\N{\rENG}I seem to have temporarily lost control.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.34,0:20:21.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,那還用說\N{\rENG}You sure did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.91,0:20:24.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,瑪麗 你還好嗎\N{\rENG}Marie, are-are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.92,0:20:27.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,還好\N{\rENG}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.92,0:20:34.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,發生什麼了\N{\rENG}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:37.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,當我們心靈融合的時候 我吸納了您的痛苦\N{\rENG}When we joined minds, I absorbed your pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.06,0:20:39.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,但我也\N{\rENG}But I also...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:40.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,我看到了什麼\N{\rENG}I saw something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.45,0:20:41.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,是的 我也是\N{\rENG}Yes, as did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:45.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,它感覺既像是您的一部分 又不是\N{\rENG}It felt both a part of you and not.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.62,0:20:46.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,是戈恩嗎\N{\rENG}Was it Gorn?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:49.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,這可能嗎\N{\rENG}Is that even possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.24,0:20:51.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,恐怕我兩個問題都無法回答 艦長\N{\rENG}I am afraid I do not have the answer to either question, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.12,0:20:58.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 史波克先生\N{\rENG}Thank you, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:21:00.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,我現在好多了\N{\rENG}The pain is much better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.06,0:21:02.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,史波克少校\N{\rENG}Lieutenant Spock,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.56,0:21:05.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,金萊利中校命令全體高級軍官到待命室報到\N{\rENG}Commander Chin-Riley needs all senior officers in the ready room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.62,0:21:07.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,我很快就來\N{\rENG}I will be there momentarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:09.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,不好意思 少尉\N{\rENG}My apologies, Ensign.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.76,0:21:16.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們可能有麻煩了\N{\rENG}We may have a situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:19.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,外勤隊沒有在預定的時間和我們通訊\N{\rENG}Our away team failed to check in at the prescheduled time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.74,0:21:21.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,他們兩人的應答器都開著\N{\rENG}Their transponders are both active,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.60,0:21:24.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,但不回應我們從進取號發出的任何呼叫\N{\rENG}but they are not responding to any hails from the Enterprise, 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.28,0:21:25.45,CHS,,0,0,0,, 換句話說\N{\rENG}which means
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:28.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,要麼是他們的通訊器出了問題\N{\rENG}they're either having comms trouble or...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.60,0:21:29.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,要麼人出了什麼事\N{\rENG}something else happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:32.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,中尉\N{\rENG}Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:34.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,佩利亞中校有時間親自前來參會嗎\N{\rENG}Does Commander Pelia plan to grace us with her presence?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.64,0:21:36.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,呃 她沒空\N{\rENG}She, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.00,0:21:37.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以派我來了\N{\rENG}got delayed and sent me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.25,0:21:40.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,好藉口 我知道她不喜歡開會\N{\rENG}Nice try. I know she hates these meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.64,0:21:41.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,請坐\N{\rENG}Sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:45.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們需要在不引起克林貢人注意的前提下\N{\rENG}We need to get within emergency beaming range
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.92,0:21:47.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,進入緊急傳送機的工作範圍\N{\rENG}without attracting any Klingon attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.84,0:21:49.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,我推薦緩慢接近\N{\rENG}I recommend a slow approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.57,0:21:53.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,以低脈衝推力航行能將我們\N{\rENG}Flying at low impulse will keep us
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.02,0:21:54.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,隱藏在碎片帶運動的背景噪聲下\N{\rENG}below the noise limit of debris motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.61,0:21:56.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,他們的傳感器將無法\N{\rENG}Their sensors will not be able
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.88,0:21:58.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,區分我們和星塵顆粒\N{\rENG}to tell us apart from the dust particles.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.32,0:22:00.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,那就是說我們只能以低脈衝推力航行\N{\rENG}Well, we'd have to move at a fraction of impulse
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.94,0:22:03.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,而且還要關掉所有非必要系統\N{\rENG}and shut down all nonessential systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.02,0:22:05.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,但如果能讓我們隱形 那倒也值得\N{\rENG}But if we were invisible, might be worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:08.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,根據我的估算 我們將需要四個小時到達肯佛瑞星\N{\rENG}By my calculations, we would reach Kenfori in four hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.02,0:22:11.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,這我能接受\N{\rENG}I can live with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.63,0:22:12.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,奧特加斯\N{\rENG}Ortegas.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.70,0:22:14.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,和史波克一起規劃一條航線\N{\rENG}Plot a course with Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.94,0:22:16.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,四個小時\N{\rENG}Four hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.98,0:22:18.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,不 我不同意\N{\rENG}Yeah, that won't work for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.94,0:22:22.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,請說明 上尉\N{\rENG}Explain yourself, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.22,0:22:24.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們幹嘛還要踮著腳躲著克林貢人\N{\rENG}Why are we tiptoeing around these Klingons?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.69,0:22:27.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,既然他們顯然已經知道姆'本加醫生和艦長在那了\N{\rENG}It's obvious they know about the captain and Dr. M'Benga.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.16,0:22:29.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們的當務之急應該是盡快把他們救出來\N{\rENG}Our priority should be getting them out fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.60,0:22:30.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,那你怎麼確保我們能夠在\N{\rENG}And how do you propose we do that
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.82,0:22:33.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,不違反邊界條約的情況下做到這點\N{\rENG}without violating a border treaty?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.04,0:22:35.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,而且 假設\N{\rENG}Hypothetically,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.40,0:22:37.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,即便有可能接近\N{\rENG}even if there were a way,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.09,0:22:38.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,星塵帶的干擾\N{\rENG}the interference from the dust belt
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.26,0:22:40.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,也會讓傳送機無法使用\N{\rENG}makes transporting impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.14,0:22:42.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,我已經想到了個辦法可以同時解決這兩個問題\N{\rENG}I've thought about both problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.12,0:22:44.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們直接曲速進行星大氣熱層裡\N{\rENG}We warp into the planet's thermosphere,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.12,0:22:47.45,Note,,0,0,0,,* 熱層是行星大氣的組成部分 高度通常為80-600千米 其下便是稠密大氣層
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.44,0:22:47.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,傳送完人 立馬曲速走 簡單\N{\rENG}energize, and warp out, simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.14,0:22:49.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,直接曲速進行星低軌道嗎\N{\rENG}Warping into a low planetary orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.94,0:22:51.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,那很魯莽了\N{\rENG}It's reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.58,0:22:53.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,你以前這麼幹過嗎\N{\rENG}Have you ever done that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.16,0:22:55.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,還沒有\N{\rENG}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.98,0:22:57.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,但我能做到\N{\rENG}But I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.20,0:23:00.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,如此危險的機動極少有人嘗試\N{\rENG}Such a dangerous maneuver is rarely attempted.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.72,0:23:02.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,我估計高層大氣沒有問題\N{\rENG}I could see the upper atmosphere maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.56,0:23:05.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,但我們只要沾到一點熱層的底\N{\rENG}But if we scrape the bottom of the thermosphere,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.16,0:23:06.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,船體就要被阻力扯成捲心菜瓣了\N{\rENG}our hull would be shredded cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.84,0:23:08.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不會讓這種事發生的\N{\rENG}I won't let that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.38,0:23:10.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,此外 殘餘曲速場同樣會干擾傳送\N{\rENG}Also, the residual warp field prohibits transport.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.92,0:23:12.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,但在理論上 穿過局部曲速場\N{\rENG}Well, in theory, one could lock in on a signal
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.73,0:23:14.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,建立傳送信號鎖定是可能的\N{\rENG}through the residual field.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.52,0:23:16.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,我沒有拆史波克先生的台的意思\N{\rENG}Well, I don't mean to step on Mr. Spock's toes,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.32,0:23:17.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,絕對沒有\N{\rENG}of course, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.14,0:23:20.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,但只需要根據曲速場的空間扭曲程度\N{\rENG}but you just have to calibrate the phase inducers
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.18,0:23:21.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,校準相位感應器\N{\rENG}to the warp distortion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.48,0:23:23.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,當然 得非常快\N{\rENG}Only, like, really fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.44,0:23:24.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,就這樣\N{\rENG}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.42,0:23:28.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以我的計劃全打鈎了\N{\rENG}So my plan checks off all the boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.18,0:23:29.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,烏乎拉 有任何跡象表明\N{\rENG}Uhura, is there any evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.74,0:23:31.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,克林貢人知道外勤隊在地表嗎\N{\rENG}the Klingons know about our people?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.18,0:23:33.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,現在是完全的通訊靜默 一點聲音都沒有\N{\rENG}Total comms silence out there, not even a whisper.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.28,0:23:39.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,那麼史波克的計劃是最合理的\N{\rENG}Then Spock's plan makes the most sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.10,0:23:40.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,命令已經下達了\N{\rENG}You have your orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.07,0:23:48.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,真謝謝你啊 妮歐塔\N{\rENG}Thanks a lot, Nyota.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.90,0:23:53.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們是不是該談談奧特加斯上尉的事\N{\rENG}Are we gonna discuss Lieutenant Ortegas?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.52,0:23:55.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,她一直想做自己擅長的事\N{\rENG}She was just doing her job.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.82,0:23:57.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,我需要後備方案\N{\rENG}I needed alternatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.56,0:23:59.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,你說了算 但我想說\N{\rENG}Your call, but, I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.10,0:24:00.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,她以前不像這樣\N{\rENG}that wasn't like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.96,0:24:03.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,她有時候可能很粗魯\N{\rENG}She can be rude at times
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.66,0:24:05.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,但絕不會不服從\N{\rENG}but not insubordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.98,0:24:08.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,會不會是太早讓她回歸崗位了\N{\rENG}Could it be she's back on rotation too soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.05,0:24:12.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,她已經過了心理關\N{\rENG}She passed her psych eval.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.08,0:24:13.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,畢竟就她的閱歷而言\N{\rENG}And after all she went through,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.26,0:24:15.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,她那有點毛躁的作風倒也在我的意料之中\N{\rENG}I'm not surprised if she's a little rough around the edges.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.64,0:24:18.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,拉安 你也明白的\N{\rENG}You get that, La'An.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.66,0:24:44.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們的傳感器壓根沒探測到這些東西\N{\rENG}Not one of those things showed up on our sensors.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.32,0:24:46.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,但它們看起來非常像活人\N{\rENG}But they looked very alive to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.42,0:24:50.01,CHS,,0,0,0,,至少 看起來不像死的\N{\rENG}At least, you know, n-not... dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.05,0:24:52.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,但無論它們是什麼\N{\rENG}Whatever they are,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.22,0:24:54.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,傳感器並不識別其為生命體徵\N{\rENG}they don't register as life signs anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.27,0:25:00.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,除了我們 這裡死氣沉沉的\N{\rENG}We are the only things moving in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.92,0:25:03.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,這可是個藏身的好地方 看\N{\rENG}This is as good a place as any to hole up. Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.80,0:25:05.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果烏娜按部執行程序的話\N{\rENG}If Una's following protocol,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.18,0:25:06.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,進取號現在就在路上了\N{\rENG}the Enterprise is already on its way.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.24,0:25:08.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們要找個通訊器\N{\rENG}We need to find comms,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.52,0:25:10.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,複製進取號的加密頻道\N{\rENG}clone the Enterprise's encrypted channel,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.82,0:25:12.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,與他們協商一個撤離點\N{\rENG}and then coordinate a rendezvous.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.20,0:25:14.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,通信陣列\N{\rENG}The comms array.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.38,0:25:18.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,它在房頂\N{\rENG}It's on the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.30,0:25:23.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,不行 上樓得和那些東西戰鬥\N{\rENG}No, we'd have to engage with those...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.66,0:25:26.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,不好聽點說 喪屍們?\N{\rENG}For serious lack of a better word, zombies?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.69,0:25:28.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,別這麼叫他們\N{\rENG}Don't call them that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.52,0:25:31.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,他們曾經是聯邦的科學家\N{\rENG}They were once Federation scientists.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.76,0:25:33.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,和克林貢人\N{\rENG}And Klingons.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.57,0:25:35.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,聽著 我很想知道這兒究竟發生了什麼\N{\rENG}Look, I'd really like to find out what happened here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.32,0:25:36.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,你可以調出實驗室的數據嗎\N{\rENG}Can you recall the lab's data?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.53,0:25:41.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,查普爾提到的作物\N{\rENG}The crops that Chapel mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.14,0:25:43.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,他們使用了奇美拉之花中的一種藥劑\N{\rENG}They used an agent from the Chimera Blossom
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.49,0:25:46.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,並用多年生苔蘚的基因對其進行基因編輯\N{\rENG}to modify them with genes from a perennial moss.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.62,0:25:49.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,這種苔蘚可以在幾乎任何環境下生長\N{\rENG}A moss that could live and grow anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.02,0:25:51.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,它們會休眠 但並不會死亡\N{\rENG}It lays dormant but never dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.07,0:25:54.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,一種雜交超級作物\N{\rENG}A hybrid supercrop.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.90,0:25:58.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,哇 這樣一來能令許多聯邦殖民果腹\N{\rENG}Wow. That would feed a lot of Federation colonists.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.96,0:26:02.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,但事態在克林貢人入侵時急轉直下\N{\rENG}Only things went to hell when the Klingons invaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.28,0:26:04.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,他們攻擊了這裡\N{\rENG}They attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.16,0:26:06.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,並無視了安全協議\N{\rENG}With no regard for safety protocols.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.30,0:26:08.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,設施中的每個人都被暴露其中\N{\rENG}And everyone in the facility was exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.86,0:26:11.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,這導致苔蘚基因組滲入人體中\N{\rENG}It inserted moss genomes into their bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.82,0:26:15.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,隨後 這種苔蘚吞噬了它周圍的所有植物\N{\rENG}This moss consumes every plant around it...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.02,0:26:17.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,以實現繁殖\N{\rENG}to proliferate.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.46,0:26:20.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,而這也是它們現在在做的\N{\rENG}And now that is what they're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.34,0:26:23.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,吞噬一切活物\N{\rENG}Devouring anything that breathes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.88,0:26:26.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,看來就是所謂的僵屍了\N{\rENG}That sounds like the "Z" word.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.93,0:26:30.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,等等 我們是不是也在吸著同樣的空氣\N{\rENG}Wait, we're breathing that same air.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.46,0:26:34.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,藥劑早就分解失效了\N{\rENG}The agent would have broken down long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.26,0:26:36.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,現在我知道你看到奇美拉之花的時候\N{\rENG}Now I see why you were so careful
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.26,0:26:37.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,為什麼要那麼小心了\N{\rENG}about that Chimera Blossom.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.42,0:26:39.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,別多想\N{\rENG}Don't overthink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.25,0:26:42.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,約瑟夫\N{\rENG}Joseph...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.18,0:26:46.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,為什麼瑪麗需要接受這樣的\N{\rENG}why would Marie need biome engineering?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.34,0:26:47.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,生物雜交工程\N{\rENG}Hybridization?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.82,0:26:53.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,史波克和我知道該如何安全使用它\N{\rENG}Spock and I know how to use it safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.88,0:26:59.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧 回答我的問題\N{\rENG}All right. Answer the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.32,0:27:01.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,你想用什麼基因和她融合\N{\rENG}You're gonna hybridize her with what?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.44,0:27:04.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,克里斯 我不能\N{\rENG}Chris, I cannot...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.16,0:27:05.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,等等 不對勁\N{\rENG}Wait, wait, wait, wait, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.97,0:27:08.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,戈恩人?\N{\rENG}The Gorn?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.42,0:27:11.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,這就是你所謂的療法嗎\N{\rENG}That's your miracle treatment?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.41,0:27:13.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,你要把瑪麗變成什麼\N{\rENG}You're g-going to turn Marie into a-a what?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.98,0:27:15.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,一個人類和戈恩人的雜交種\N{\rENG}A human-Gorn hybrid?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.30,0:27:16.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,根本不是這樣\N{\rENG}It is not that rudimentary.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.62,0:27:17.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,那就解釋給我聽\N{\rENG}Then explain it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.76,0:27:19.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我跟你說過了\N{\rENG}I already told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.98,0:27:22.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,這是救活她的唯一方法\N{\rENG}it is her only chance of survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.54,0:27:26.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,讓我理解一下\N{\rENG}Let me understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.48,0:27:28.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,比起清除她身上的戈恩遺傳物質\N{\rENG}Instead of ridding her body of the Gorn DNA,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.78,0:27:30.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,現在反而要讓它永遠留在她體內\N{\rENG}you're gonna make it permanent?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.30,0:27:34.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,你想要對她進行基因改造\N{\rENG}You're going to change her?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.32,0:27:36.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,告訴我\N{\rENG}Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.64,0:27:37.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,約瑟夫\N{\rENG}Joseph...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.28,0:27:41.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,告訴我 你到底要對她做什麼\N{\rENG}Just... what are you going to do to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.00,0:27:43.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,這是她自己的選擇 克里斯\N{\rENG}It was her decision, Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.40,0:27:46.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,她選擇如此\N{\rENG}She chose this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.40,0:27:51.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,她不想讓你告訴我\N{\rENG}She didn't want you to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.49,0:27:57.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以史波克才主動提出和你一起去\N{\rENG}That's why you and Spock wanted to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.84,0:27:59.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,這樣一來我就永遠不會得知\N{\rENG}So I would never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.22,0:28:00.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\rENG}Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.16,0:28:02.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,這是救活她的唯一方法\N{\rENG}This is the only way to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.76,0:28:08.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,而這也是我們都想要的結果\N{\rENG}And that is what we all want.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.06,0:28:09.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,這就是你救她的辦法嗎\N{\rENG}This is your idea of saving--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.36,0:28:11.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,還說什麼我們都想要的\N{\rENG}Wh-What we all want?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.56,0:28:12.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,絕對不是\N{\rENG}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.51,0:28:14.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,再復盤一下\N{\rENG}Look again.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.46,0:28:16.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,再努力努力\N{\rENG}Try harder. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.40,0:28:18.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,肯定有別的方法的\N{\rENG}There's got to be another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.56,0:28:20.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,她只有幾天時間了\N{\rENG}She has a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.70,0:28:22.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,可能更少\N{\rENG}Maybe less.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.61,0:28:25.05,CHS,,0,0,0,,幾天\N{\rENG}A few days?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.05,0:28:26.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,她不想讓我知道\N{\rENG}She didn't want me to know
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.40,0:28:27.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,她也不想告訴我\N{\rENG}and she didn't want to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.86,0:28:28.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,為什麼\N{\rENG}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.88,0:28:36.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們要被圍堵了\N{\rENG}We're gonna get swarmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.28,0:28:37.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,過載槍上的供能線圈\N{\rENG}Overload the charging coil.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.28,0:29:16.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,你們跟我們走\N{\rENG}You will come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.00,0:29:20.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,謝謝你\N{\rENG}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.94,0:29:23.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,你是誰呢\N{\rENG}Uh, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.04,0:29:24.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,拿著裂解槍的人\N{\rENG}The one holding a disruptor.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.33,0:29:36.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,走我前面\N{\rENG}Ahead of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.52,0:29:38.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,要是走錯一步 你們就都得死\N{\rENG}One wrong step and you both die.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.88,0:29:40.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rENG}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.24,0:29:44.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,至少你不會生吞活剝了我們\N{\rENG}At least you're not trying to eat us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.92,0:29:53.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,往前走\N{\rENG}Forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.40,0:30:19.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,可多虧你把它們搞醒了\N{\rENG}Thanks for waking them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.52,0:30:35.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,它們數量太多了\N{\rENG}There are too many!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.50,0:30:36.92,CHS,,0,0,0,,那些是力場發生器\N{\rENG}Those are forcefield emitters.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.92,0:30:38.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,控制台就在正中央\N{\rENG}The console's dead center!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.66,0:30:42.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,約瑟夫\N{\rENG}Joseph?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.92,0:30:57.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們能試著把他們引開穿梭機\N{\rENG}We could try luring them away from your shuttle,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.22,0:30:57.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,然後關閉力場逃離\N{\rENG}and then lowering the field,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.90,0:30:59.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,但我們需要武器\N{\rENG}but we need weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.21,0:31:11.20,CHS,,0,0,0,,克里斯\N{\rENG}Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.66,0:31:14.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,我真是嘴欠才找你合作\N{\rENG}I walked right into that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.38,0:31:15.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,你到底是誰\N{\rENG}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.36,0:31:17.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,先說說你是誰吧\N{\rENG}First, we talk about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.28,0:31:20.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不得不說 當你們的穿梭機越過邊界時\N{\rENG}I have to say, when your shuttle crossed the treaty line,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.40,0:31:22.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,我簡直難以置信\N{\rENG}I couldn't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.14,0:31:24.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,我還以為是我的維瑞迪姆定位器壞了\N{\rENG}I thought my viridium tracker was broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.54,0:31:25.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,你在追蹤他?\N{\rENG}You were tracking him?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.52,0:31:27.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,下次隆'戈維亞人請你喝酒的時候\N{\rENG}When a R'ongovian offers you a drink,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.84,0:31:29.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,記得別吃掉裡面的橄欖\N{\rENG}never eat the olives.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.22,0:31:32.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,現在你找到我了 但為什麼\N{\rENG}Now you found me. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.38,0:31:34.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,你沒有看見嗎\N{\rENG}Do you not see a reflection?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.71,0:31:37.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,一束來自宿敵的目光\N{\rENG}The gaze of an old enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.46,0:31:41.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,我殺了太多克林貢人\N{\rENG}I have killed too many Klingons
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.10,0:31:43.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,以至於我都不知道你來自哪個家族\N{\rENG}to know which house you're from.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.00,0:31:45.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,我是拜莎\N{\rENG}I am Bytha.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.38,0:31:49.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,達克'拉赫的女兒 拉烏爾家族的冠軍戰士\N{\rENG}Daughter of Dak'Rah, champion of House Rah'Ul.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.84,0:31:51.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,拉赫大使的女兒\N{\rENG}Ambassador Rah's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.36,0:31:55.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,約瑟夫·姆'本加\N{\rENG}Joseph M'Benga...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.02,0:31:57.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,我來這是為了讓你為\N{\rENG}I am here to make you answer
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.80,0:31:59.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,被你刺殺的克林貢人付出代價\N{\rENG}for the Klingon you assassinated.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.46,0:32:08.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,正在進入肯佛瑞周圍的緩衝區\N{\rENG}We are now entering the buffer zone around Kenfori.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.38,0:32:13.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,這是一種儀式\N{\rENG}It's a ritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.54,0:32:16.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,上尉 保持七分之一脈衝推力\N{\rENG}Lieutenant, keep the ship at one-seventh impulse,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.45,0:32:17.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,但也不要空轉\N{\rENG}and not a tick over.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.58,0:32:19.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,高於此速度會暴露我們的位置\N{\rENG}Anything above that will give away our position.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.52,0:32:21.67,CHS,,0,0,0,,遵命 中校 保持速度\N{\rENG}Aye, Commander. Maintaining speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.67,0:32:23.07,CHS,,0,0,0,,艦橋呼叫輪機部\N{\rENG}Bridge to Engineering.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.07,0:32:24.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,關閉所有非必要系統\N{\rENG}Power down all non-essential systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.55,0:32:29.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,正在接近克林貢戰列巡洋艦 距離兩百公里\N{\rENG}Approaching the battle cruiser at 200 kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.06,0:32:30.77,CHS,,0,0,0,,有視訊了\N{\rENG}I have a visual.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.17,0:32:39.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,抱歉 龜速之下我很難機動\N{\rENG}Sorry. It's hard to maneuver at snail speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.16,0:32:41.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,距離克林貢戰巡一百公里\N{\rENG}Battle Cruiser at 100 kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.44,0:33:04.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們已經遠離克林貢戰巡\N{\rENG}We are clear of the Klingon ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.00,0:33:06.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,通訊如何\N{\rENG}Comms?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.78,0:33:08.37,CHS,,0,0,0,,沒有檢測到任何訊息\N{\rENG}Not picking up any chatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.78,0:33:10.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,護盾狀態如何\N{\rENG}Shields?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.08,0:33:12.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,仍然關閉 他們看不到我們\N{\rENG}Still down. They can't see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.34,0:33:17.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,檢測到低溫凝華現象\N{\rENG}Detecting frozen volatiles forming.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.20,0:33:21.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,建議將速度降至八分之一脈衝\N{\rENG}Recommend reducing speed to one-eighth impulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.08,0:33:23.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,預計抵達時間修改為六小時\N{\rENG}Amending estimated arrival to six hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.30,0:33:29.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們必須相信派克和姆'本加\N{\rENG}We'll have to trust that Pike and M'Benga are capable enough
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.87,0:33:31.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,能夠再堅持多一會\N{\rENG}to hold down their own a little while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.56,0:33:34.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,上尉 降至八分之一脈衝推力\N{\rENG}Lieutenant, one-eighth impulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.84,0:33:37.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,已減速至八分之一\N{\rENG}Slowing to one-eighth.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.20,0:33:46.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,中校 我檢測到一些信號\N{\rENG}Commander, I'm picking up something now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.93,0:33:48.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,是一個監測頻率\N{\rENG}It's a monitoring frequency.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.66,0:33:50.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,他們的傳感器正在啟動\N{\rENG}Their sensors are activating.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.28,0:33:52.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,他們正在將傳感陣列瞄向我艦\N{\rENG}They're turning their array toward our ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.85,0:33:55.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,中校 我想我們被發現了\N{\rENG}Commander, I think we've been spotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.95,0:34:03.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,沒事的 我會活下來\N{\rENG}It's fine. I'll survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.52,0:34:07.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,夠了 離開他\N{\rENG}Enough. Leave him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.35,0:34:12.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,冤有頭 債有主 饒了我的朋友吧\N{\rENG}Your grievance is with me. Spare my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.18,0:34:14.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,你錯了\N{\rENG}You are wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.44,0:34:18.09,CHS,,0,0,0,,我的冤一直在我父親身上\N{\rENG}My grievance has always been with my father,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.09,0:34:19.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,他是帝國的叛徒\N{\rENG}traitor to the empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.80,0:34:21.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,你不是來為他報仇的?\N{\rENG}You're not here to avenge him?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.49,0:34:22.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,他是個戰犯\N{\rENG}He was a war criminal
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.78,0:34:25.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,也是投降聯邦的走狗\N{\rENG}and a lapdog to the Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.80,0:34:27.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,死有餘辜\N{\rENG}I welcomed his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.26,0:34:29.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,原來是克林貢人的血仇\N{\rENG}A Klingon blood feud.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.44,0:34:36.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,達克'拉赫讓我們家族蒙羞\N{\rENG}Dak'Rah brought shame to our family name.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.04,0:34:37.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,因為他的罪\N{\rENG}For his sins,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.24,0:34:40.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們家族受盡屈辱\N{\rENG}our house has been subject to discommendation.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.25,0:34:43.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,族人被疏遠 血統被唾棄\N{\rENG}We are shunned, our bloodline spat upon.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.12,0:34:45.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,甚至 為了包船來這裡 我不得不卑躬屈膝\N{\rENG}I had to grovel just to charter a ship here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.73,0:34:49.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,只有一種方法可以恢復我們的名譽\N{\rENG}There was one way to restore our name.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.68,0:34:51.42,CHS,,0,0,0,,親手暗殺我的父親\N{\rENG}Assassinate my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.42,0:34:53.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,可惡的是 你先殺掉了他\N{\rENG}Only, you got to him first.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.66,0:34:57.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rENG}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.58,0:34:59.83,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們需要保持冷靜\N{\rENG}We need to stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.83,0:35:01.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,她認為殺了我\N{\rENG}She thinks killing me
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.44,0:35:04.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,會以某種方式恢復她的榮譽\N{\rENG}will somehow restore her honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.24,0:35:06.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,除非我手刃刺殺我父親的刺客\N{\rENG}Our name remains soiled
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.58,0:35:08.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,否則我們的家族仍將蒙羞\N{\rENG}unless I kill my father's assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.32,0:35:10.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,儀式戰鬥?\N{\rENG}Ritual combat?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.06,0:35:13.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,戰鬥至死?\N{\rENG}To the death?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.50,0:35:15.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,他沒有暗殺拉赫\N{\rENG}He didn't assassinate Rah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.93,0:35:17.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,他的行為是出於自衛\N{\rENG}He acted in self-defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.33,0:35:19.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,這個人類說的是實話嗎\N{\rENG}Does this human speak the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.16,0:35:21.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,你的戰士時代已經過去了嗎\N{\rENG}Are your warrior days behind you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.94,0:35:27.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,我只問你一次\N{\rENG}I will only ask you once.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.50,0:35:29.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,你真的暗殺了我父親嗎\N{\rENG}Did you assassinate my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.28,0:35:34.87,CHS,,0,0,0,,他們把我們掃描了個遍\N{\rENG}Their scanners are all over us.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.87,0:35:36.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,-烏乎拉 -還是什麼也沒有\N{\rENG}- Uhura. - Still nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.36,0:35:37.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,克林貢人沒有回應\N{\rENG}The Klingons aren't responding.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.76,0:35:38.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,繼續嘗試\N{\rENG}Keep trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.80,0:35:40.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,告訴他們我們來這裡執行救援任務\N{\rENG}Inform them that we are here on a rescue mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.44,0:35:41.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們並沒有著陸意圖\N{\rENG}We are not attempting to land.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.94,0:35:43.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,他們還沒有升起護盾\N{\rENG}They haven't raised shields yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.26,0:35:45.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,但我建議趁我們還有機會 升起護盾\N{\rENG}but I recommend raising ours while we have the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.23,0:35:47.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,不行 這樣會釋放錯誤的信號\N{\rENG}No, that sends the wrong message.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.92,0:35:50.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,為什麼要關心他們的看法\N{\rENG}Why do we care what they think?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.38,0:35:51.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,這毫無意義 如果他們\N{\rENG}This is pointless. If they...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.60,0:35:58.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,說完你的想法 上尉\N{\rENG}Finish your thought, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.24,0:36:00.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,我只是認為我們已經越過了外交能解決的界限\N{\rENG}I just think we're past the point of diplomacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.64,0:36:03.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,你認為向我表達這種擔憂是明智的嗎\N{\rENG}And you thought it wise to express that concern to me
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.11,0:36:04.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,鑑於我們正在執行命令的過程中?\N{\rENG}in the middle of executing orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.42,0:36:08.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}克林貢艦船護盾已升起
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.44,0:36:11.73,CHS,,0,0,0,,克林貢戰巡正在升起護盾並逼近\N{\rENG}The Klingons are raising shields and closing in.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.46,0:36:15.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,中校 是時候交戰了\N{\rENG}Commander, time to engage.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.58,0:36:17.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,執行規避機動 奧特加斯 看你了\N{\rENG}Evasive maneuvers. Ortegas, you're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.91,0:36:20.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,樂意之至\N{\rENG}Gladly.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.83,0:36:26.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,告訴她真相\N{\rENG}Just tell her the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.70,0:36:30.71,CHS,,0,0,0,,我暗殺了拉赫\N{\rENG}I assassinated Rah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.71,0:36:32.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,-約瑟夫 -我本可以阻止自己\N{\rENG}- Joseph... - I could have stopped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.14,0:36:34.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,但這個大屠殺兇手給了我\N{\rENG}But a mass murderer gave me
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.14,0:36:36.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,殺死他的機會\N{\rENG}the opportunity to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.56,0:36:38.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,我如此做了\N{\rENG}And I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.80,0:36:41.14,CHS,,0,0,0,,自願的\N{\rENG}Willingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.46,0:36:43.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果再有機會 我還會如此\N{\rENG}I would do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.50,0:36:46.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以 沒錯\N{\rENG}So yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.29,0:36:48.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,他的性命 由我奪取\N{\rENG}His blood is on my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.94,0:36:51.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,這是不光彩的嗎\N{\rENG}Was that dishonorable?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.94,0:36:53.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,我不清楚\N{\rENG}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.38,0:36:57.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,但我清楚 那是正義\N{\rENG}But there was justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.08,0:36:59.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,我撒謊 是為了掩護\N{\rENG}I lied to protect
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.43,0:37:01.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,那個仍潛藏於我內心的野獸\N{\rENG}the monster that still lives inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.20,0:37:07.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,若有需要 我會讓他重拾鋒鏑\N{\rENG}Should the day come when he is needed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.40,0:37:15.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,把刀拿起來\N{\rENG}Pick up the blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.97,0:37:17.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,直面我\N{\rENG}And face me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.60,0:37:28.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,約瑟夫\N{\rENG}Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.85,0:37:30.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,別這樣\N{\rENG}Don't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.10,0:37:31.85,CHS,,0,0,0,,我包裡有一個給你的醫療包\N{\rENG}There is a med kit for you in my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.85,0:37:33.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,找到辦法離開這個遺棄星球\N{\rENG}Find your way off this forsaken planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.26,0:37:36.06,CHS,,0,0,0,,然後把花帶給巴特爾艦長\N{\rENG}and get the flower to Batel.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.06,0:37:37.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,查普爾護士和史波克那裡有我的實驗記錄\N{\rENG}Chapel and Spock have my lab notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.86,0:37:38.98,CHS,,0,0,0,,一定有其他方法\N{\rENG}There has to be another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.98,0:37:39.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,夠了\N{\rENG}Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.34,0:37:43.43,CHS,,0,0,0,,是時候了 你死我活\N{\rENG}It is time for one of us to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.26,0:37:49.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,我已經準備好面對我的命運了\N{\rENG}I am ready to face my destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.57,0:37:51.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,你呢\N{\rENG}Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.79,0:37:59.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,上面沾有我父親的血\N{\rENG}This holds the blood of my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.88,0:38:03.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,把他纏在手上\N{\rENG}It binds us.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.10,0:38:06.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,直到它沾滿敗者的鮮血\N{\rENG}Until it is stained with the blood of the vanquished.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.56,0:39:13.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rENG}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.30,0:39:15.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rENG}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.79,0:39:20.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,你不能棄權\N{\rENG}You cannot forfeit!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.18,0:39:23.26,CHS,,0,0,0,,太遲了\N{\rENG}Too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.56,0:39:26.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,我今天不需要釋放野獸出來\N{\rENG}I do not need the monster today.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.52,0:39:28.19,CHS,,0,0,0,,輕饒我命\N{\rENG}By sparing my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.19,0:39:30.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,是對我的命運下了詛咒 比死了還糟糕\N{\rENG}you damn me to a fate worse than death.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.00,0:39:33.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,這力場要支撐不住了\N{\rENG}That field's about to come down.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.84,0:39:43.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,斯坎內爾中尉 還有多久\N{\rENG}Lieutenant Scannell, time?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.16,0:39:44.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,四秒後進入大氣熱層\N{\rENG}Thermospheric entry in four seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.59,0:39:46.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,外部氣體壓縮到80%\N{\rENG}Outer gas compression is at 80%.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.30,0:39:48.25,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以我們基本上算是撞向一堵磚牆\N{\rENG}So basically we're flying into a brick wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.25,0:39:49.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,別亂想了 堅守崗位\N{\rENG}Don't think about it, just hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.52,0:40:00.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,傳送室呼叫艦橋\N{\rENG}Transporter to Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.74,0:40:02.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,你們必須立刻關閉引擎\N{\rENG}You need to cut engine power now!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.52,0:40:04.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果你們不補償行星引力\N{\rENG}If you don't compensate for planetary gravity,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.62,0:40:05.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,船會散架的\N{\rENG}we will come apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.84,0:40:06.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,收到 中尉 \N{\rENG}Copy, Lieutenant. 
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.94,0:40:08.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,你繼續嘗試獲取傳送信號\N{\rENG}You work on getting us that transporter signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.90,0:40:11.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,佩利亞早就警告過你別逞強\N{\rENG}Pelia warned you not to volunteer.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.08,0:40:13.75,CHS,,0,0,0,,現在好了 說出去的話就像潑出去的水\N{\rENG}And now you actually have to do what you promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.84,0:40:36.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,力場重新上線了 但是它撐不了太久\N{\rENG}The field is back up, but it won't hold much longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.92,0:40:50.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,目前你殺了一個\N{\rENG}You got one.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.86,0:40:52.10,CHS,,0,0,0,,你還有心情記分啊\N{\rENG}You're keeping score?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.32,0:41:00.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,聽著\N{\rENG}Listen, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.84,0:41:03.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們合作 就能都活著逃出去\N{\rENG}we work together, we all get out alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.50,0:41:23.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}衝我來
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.62,0:41:25.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}你們這些骯髒的塔格獸
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.50,0:41:29.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,她在吸引喪屍的注意\N{\rENG}She's drawing their attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.53,0:41:30.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,為什麼\N{\rENG}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.53,0:41:33.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,通過犧牲她自己\N{\rENG}By sacrificing herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.53,0:41:35.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,她會光榮地死去\N{\rENG}she chooses an honorable death.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.44,0:41:36.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是沒有人會知道\N{\rENG}But no one will ever know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.66,0:41:38.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,她會知道\N{\rENG}She will know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.28,0:41:42.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,我會知道\N{\rENG}I will know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.82,0:41:44.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,願斯托沃寇歡迎你\N{\rENG}May Sto-vo-kor welcome you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.82,0:41:46.34,Note,,0,0,0,,* 斯托沃寇是克林貢人光榮死去後會去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.42,0:41:56.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,快走 到穿梭機上去\N{\rENG}Come on, let's get to the shuttle.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.80,0:41:59.30,CHS,tag,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}甲板重力層失效
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.80,0:41:59.51,CHS,,0,0,0,,輪機室發出警告\N{\rENG}Alert from Engineering!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.51,0:42:00.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,人工重力正在失效\N{\rENG}Artificial gravity is failing
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.88,0:42:02.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,慣性阻尼器效能僅剩20%\N{\rENG}and inertial dampeners are at 20%.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.64,0:42:04.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果我們不讓它重新上線\N{\rENG}If we don't get it back up...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.65,0:42:11.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,奧特加斯 你能穩定我們的軌道嗎\N{\rENG}Ortegas, can you stabilize us?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.00,0:42:12.46,CHS,,0,0,0,,稍等\N{\rENG}In a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.46,0:42:13.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,傳送室呼叫艦橋\N{\rENG}Transport to Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.76,0:42:17.58,CHS,,0,0,0,,在艦船軌道塌陷時 很難保持模式完整性\N{\rENG}It's a little hard to maintain pattern integrity in orbital collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.58,0:42:19.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,你們能不能稍微開穩一點\N{\rENG}Can you maybe give me a smidge less turbulence?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.64,0:42:21.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,斯考特 你知道怎麼重新穩定軌道嗎\N{\rENG}Mr. Scott, any ideas on how to re-stabilize?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.86,0:42:24.74,CHS,,0,0,0,,試試交替啟動脈衝引擎\N{\rENG}Try firing impulse thrusters in an alternating pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.74,0:42:26.70,CHS,,0,0,0,,先啟動輔助引擎 再啟動主引擎\N{\rENG}Auxiliary first, then the main.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.70,0:42:28.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我要開始傳送了\N{\rENG}I'm gonna energize.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.00,0:42:29.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,我真心希望自己不要把\N{\rENG}I really hope I don't scramble
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.80,0:42:32.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,艦長和姆'本加醫生混在一起了\N{\rENG}the captain and Dr. M'Benga up.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.78,0:42:54.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,傳送室呼叫艦橋\N{\rENG}Transport to Bridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.82,0:42:56.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,艦長和醫官已經傳送登艦\N{\rENG}we have the captain and doctor on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.52,0:42:58.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,幹得好 斯考提 我們現在維持在軌道上\N{\rENG}Good one, Scotty. We're maintaining orbit now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.36,0:43:00.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,中校 我們的通訊受到干擾\N{\rENG}Commander, I'm getting interference on our comms.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.90,0:43:01.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,有東西在阻塞我們的通訊\N{\rENG}Something's jamming us.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.96,0:43:02.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,來源不是星塵帶\N{\rENG}It's not from the dust belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.88,0:43:03.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,打開艦尾視訊\N{\rENG}Aft viewscreen.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.20,0:43:07.41,CHS,,0,0,0,,他們正在進入攻擊陣位\N{\rENG}They're on an attack course.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.41,0:43:08.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,奧特加斯\N{\rENG}Ortegas?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.36,0:43:09.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,馬上就好\N{\rENG}Already on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.28,0:43:11.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,吃我們的尾氣去吧\N{\rENG}Say hi to our dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.12,0:43:20.63,CHS,,0,0,0,,恭喜 各位\N{\rENG}Congratulations, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.42,0:43:25.22,CHS,,0,0,0,,艾麗卡 相當精彩的飛行\N{\rENG}Erica... stellar flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.22,0:43:26.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,但下次別這麼做了\N{\rENG}But never do that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.34,0:43:34.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,艦長個人日誌 補充\N{\rENG}Captain's personal log, supplemental.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.56,0:43:36.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們已經帶著一朵奇美拉之花\N{\rENG}We have returned from our away mission
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.36,0:43:37.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,從外遣任務歸來\N{\rENG}with a single Chimera Blossom.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.35,0:43:40.79,CHS,,0,0,0,,一旦史波克完成了化合物的合成\N{\rENG}Once Spock synthesizes its chemical compounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.79,0:43:42.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,瑪麗就可以開始接受新療法了\N{\rENG}Marie's new therapy can begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.40,0:43:45.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,我好奇這個激進的療法\N{\rENG}I wonder what effects this radical treatment
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.64,0:43:47.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,對她會有什麼效果\N{\rENG}will have on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.62,0:43:52.84,CHS,,0,0,0,,你會上報我的行徑嗎\N{\rENG}Are you going to turn me in?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.41,0:43:58.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,你擔心我會嗎\N{\rENG}Are you worried I will?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.68,0:44:03.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,那取決於我在跟誰說話\N{\rENG}That depends on who I'm talking to right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.30,0:44:05.86,CHS,,0,0,0,,是我的朋友\N{\rENG}My friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.86,0:44:07.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,還是我的艦長\N{\rENG}or my captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.84,0:44:10.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,我理解你為什麼有些事\N{\rENG}Look, I understand why you didn't tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.03,0:44:11.52,CHS,,0,0,0,,不肯告訴我了\N{\rENG}certain things, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.64,0:44:15.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,我只希望我能早些知道\N{\rENG}I just wish I had known some of them sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.28,0:44:19.02,CHS,,0,0,0,,按照官方說法\N{\rENG}Officially, there was
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.02,0:44:20.91,CHS,,0,0,0,,不存在前往肯佛瑞星的任務\N{\rENG}no mission to Kenfori.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.91,0:44:22.64,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以 那裡什麼也沒有發生\N{\rENG}So, nothing happened there.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.84,0:44:25.68,CHS,,0,0,0,,我沒有什麼報告需要提交\N{\rENG}I don't have any report to file.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.72,0:44:28.11,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是如果假設\N{\rENG}But if you did,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.74,0:44:30.62,CHS,,0,0,0,,你提交了報告\N{\rENG}hypothetically,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.62,0:44:32.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,裡面會怎麼說\N{\rENG}what would it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.40,0:44:34.88,CHS,,0,0,0,,會說 有人用刀架在我喉嚨上\N{\rENG}That I had a knife to my throat and 
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.88,0:44:36.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,你為了救我 編了一個故事\N{\rENG}you told a story to save my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.67,0:44:40.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,那就是事情的經過 有異議嗎\N{\rENG}That's what happened, wouldn't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.16,0:44:45.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,沒有\N{\rENG}I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.55,0:44:51.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,你不是一頭野獸 約瑟夫\N{\rENG}You're not a monster, Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.38,0:44:56.21,CHS,,0,0,0,,只是一個普通人\N{\rENG}Just a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.21,0:44:58.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,更是我的朋友\N{\rENG}And my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.22,0:45:08.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 你想聊聊嗎\N{\rENG}What's up? You wanted to chat?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.00,0:45:10.89,CHS,,0,0,0,,請就座 上尉\N{\rENG}Have a seat, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.89,0:45:13.66,CHS,,0,0,0,,感覺 很正式啊\N{\rENG}Oh, this feels, uh, official.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.49,0:45:17.56,CHS,,0,0,0,,正好在0240時\N{\rENG}At precisely 0240 hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.56,0:45:19.48,CHS,,0,0,0,,當我嚴令你保持脈衝引擎推力在八分之一時\N{\rENG}you pushed the engines to one-sixth impulse power,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.48,0:45:21.29,CHS,,0,0,0,,你把它開到了六分之一推力\N{\rENG}when I gave you strict orders to keep us at one-eighth.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.68,0:45:25.55,CHS,,0,0,0,,我在試圖躲避小行星\N{\rENG}I was trying to dodge tiny asteroids.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.24,0:45:28.17,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們當時都很緊張\N{\rENG}We were all on edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.17,0:45:29.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,我可能有點手滑了\N{\rENG}My finger might have slipped a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.20,0:45:31.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,我相信對一般舵手來說\N{\rENG}A reasonable error by the standards
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.93,0:45:33.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,這是個合情合理的錯誤\N{\rENG}I hold most helm officers to.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.53,0:45:35.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,但你不是一般的舵手\N{\rENG}But you're not most helm officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.08,0:45:37.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,你不會犯這樣的錯誤\N{\rENG}You don't make mistakes like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.57,0:45:40.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,除非你是有意為之\N{\rENG}Unless they're intentional.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.97,0:45:43.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,你逼我做出決定\N{\rENG}You forced my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.44,0:45:47.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,你開得剛好快到能讓我們被克林貢人發現\N{\rENG}You flew just fast enough for us to be spotted by the Klingons,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.93,0:45:51.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,所以我別無選擇 只能轉而執行你的計劃\N{\rENG}so I'd have no choice but to switch over to your plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.12,0:45:52.57,CHS,,0,0,0,,看著我的眼睛\N{\rENG}Look me in the eye
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.57,0:45:54.33,CHS,,0,0,0,,告訴我 我想錯了\N{\rENG}and tell me I'm wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.01,0:45:58.36,CHS,,0,0,0,,你打算讓派克和姆'本加\N{\rENG}You were going to leave Pike and M'Benga
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.36,0:46:00.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,被困在下面六個小時\N{\rENG}stranded for six hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.08,0:46:02.54,CHS,,0,0,0,,我們都知道克林貢人不收俘虜\N{\rENG}We all know the Klingons don't take prisoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.54,0:46:04.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,你可以不同意我的決策\N{\rENG}Disagree with me all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.00,0:46:05.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,但不是你來做出決策\N{\rENG}It's not your call to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.76,0:46:07.45,CHS,,0,0,0,,你知道六個小時能發生什麼嗎\N{\rENG}Do you know what could happen in six hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.63,0:46:15.03,CHS,,0,0,0,,對你的遭遇 我感到很遺憾\N{\rENG}I'm sorry about what happened to you, Erica.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.03,0:46:16.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是我不能讓這些事影響你的判斷\N{\rENG}But I can't have it affect your judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.72,0:46:18.28,CHS,,0,0,0,,那是個錯誤\N{\rENG}It was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.02,0:46:20.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,我能處理好它\N{\rENG}I can get a handle on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.76,0:46:22.47,CHS,,0,0,0,,你最好能\N{\rENG}You better.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.47,0:46:24.65,CHS,,0,0,0,,派克和姆'本加當時正準備開穿梭機逃走\N{\rENG}Pike and M'Benga were about to escape in a shuttle.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.65,0:46:26.30,CHS,,0,0,0,,你耍的花招不必要地威脅到了\N{\rENG}So your maneuver endangered
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.30,0:46:27.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,艦上每一個人的安全\N{\rENG}everyone on the ship unnecessarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.96,0:46:31.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,我並沒有想危及他們\N{\rENG}I never meant to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.48,0:46:33.61,CHS,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\rENG}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.64,0:46:37.96,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是你抗命是有後果的\N{\rENG}But there are consequences for insubordination.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.96,0:46:40.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,我會把你從輪班表上撤下\N{\rENG}I'm pulling you from the duty roster.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.32,0:46:41.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,兩週時間\N{\rENG}Two weeks. 
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.40,0:46:43.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,在此期間內 你需要向准尉報道\N{\rENG}In that time, you'll have to report to the warrant officer
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.18,0:46:44.44,CHS,,0,0,0,,進行指揮體系訓練\N{\rENG}for Chain-of-Command training.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.13,0:46:53.93,CHS,,0,0,0,,我可以離開了嗎 長官\N{\rENG}Am I dismissed, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.77,0:47:00.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,艾麗卡\N{\rENG}Erica.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.86,0:47:03.16,CHS,,0,0,0,,什麼事 長官\N{\rENG}Yes, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.25,0:47:06.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,這種事不能再發生了\N{\rENG}This can't ever happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.24,0:47:09.72,CHS,,0,0,0,,你明白嗎\N{\rENG}You do realize that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.89,0:47:11.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,我明白\N{\rENG}I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.35,0:47:15.13,CHS,,0,0,0,,而且我很抱歉\N{\rENG}And I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.71,0:47:32.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\rENG}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.24,0:47:34.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,你的腿怎麼樣了 我聽說你受傷了\N{\rENG}How's your leg? I heard you got hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.04,0:47:34.97,CHS,,0,0,0,,沒事了\N{\rENG}It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.68,0:47:41.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,我想知道為什麼船上除了我以外\N{\rENG}I want to know why everyone else on the ship
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.24,0:47:42.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,所有人都知道這件事\N{\rENG}seems to know but me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.56,0:47:44.78,CHS,,0,0,0,,當那植物把你和幾乎殺死你的物種\N{\rENG}Do you have any idea what could happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.78,0:47:46.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,融合在一起的時候\N{\rENG}When that plant fuses you with the species
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.49,0:47:47.69,CHS,,0,0,0,,你知道後果可能有多嚴重嗎\N{\rENG}that nearly killed you already?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.69,0:47:49.34,CHS,,0,0,0,,我清楚所有的風險\N{\rENG}I know all the risks and...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.90,0:47:50.81,CHS,,0,0,0,,但我不在乎\N{\rENG}I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.81,0:47:52.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,你對我說謊了\N{\rENG}Fine, you lied to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.04,0:47:53.18,CHS,,0,0,0,,我從來沒對你說過謊\N{\rENG}I never lied to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.18,0:47:54.12,CHS,,0,0,0,,那你為什麼不告訴我\N{\rENG}Then why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.12,0:47:55.50,CHS,,0,0,0,,原因在於你\N{\rENG}Because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.65,0:47:59.82,CHS,,0,0,0,,因為這件事 因為我已經沒有餘裕去顧慮\N{\rENG}Because of this, because I don't have the space to worry
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.82,0:48:01.60,CHS,,0,0,0,,我的死會如何讓你難過\N{\rENG}about how my dying hurts your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.58,0:48:14.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,克里斯\N{\rENG}Chris?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.60,0:48:17.24,CHS,,0,0,0,,你還有好幾天時間\N{\rENG}You had days and...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.24,0:48:19.59,CHS,,0,0,0,,但你做出了我能想像的\N{\rENG}you made what I can only imagine
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.59,0:48:21.53,CHS,,0,0,0,,你人生中最艱難的決定\N{\rENG}is the hardest decision of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.53,0:48:23.04,CHS,,0,0,0,,我卻沒參與其中\N{\rENG}But I wasn't a part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.04,0:48:24.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,是的 因為這與你無關\N{\rENG} Yeah, because it wasn't about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.00,0:48:26.32,CHS,,0,0,0,,我只希望我有機會能說出所有該說的話\N{\rENG}I just wish I'd have had the opportunity to be able to say
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.32,0:48:28.80,CHS,,0,0,0,,有機會告訴你 我會無條件支持你\N{\rENG}all the right things, to tell you I'd be there no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.80,0:48:29.90,CHS,,0,0,0,,無論你做了什麼決定\N{\rENG}No matter what choice you made.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.90,0:48:30.94,CHS,,0,0,0,,如果真是那樣就好了\N{\rENG}And that would've been nicer.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.94,0:48:33.38,CHS,,0,0,0,,但是你知道嗎 你我都心知肚明\N{\rENG}But you know what, we both know you and we know
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.38,0:48:35.40,CHS,,0,0,0,,你一定會堅持要我們尋找別的辦法\N{\rENG}that you would have demanded we find another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.65,0:48:40.08,CHS,,0,0,0,,然而並沒有別的辦法了\N{\rENG}And there is no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.64,0:48:43.00,CHS,,0,0,0,,我很害怕 克里斯\N{\rENG}I'm scared, Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.00,0:48:45.35,CHS,,0,0,0,,嘿 過來\N{\rENG}Hey, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.35,0:48:46.76,CHS,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\rENG}I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.57,0:48:52.49,CHS,,0,0,0,,我也很害怕\N{\rENG}I'm scared, too.
